Async-compatible structured logging middleware capturing method, path, view name, query count, response time, and status code as JSON log entries. Identifies 3 files to modify, 3 new types needed, integration via middleware stack, and 5 realistic risks (performance, query counting, async compatibility, circular imports, PII sensitivity).

